      "type": "file",
      "name": "LicenseSelector.vue",
      "filePath": "frontend/src/components/work/LicenseSelector.vue",
      "summary": "知识产权许可证选择器：提供 CC BY/CC BY-SA/CC BY-NC 等知识共享协议和自定义许可证选项，自动填充对应权利开关。",
      "tags": ["vue-component", "license", "creative-commons", "rights-management"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "内含 LICENSE_DEFAULTS 字典将许可证值映射到 allow_reproduction/allow_derivatives/allow_commercial 三个布尔标志。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:frontend/src/components/work/ProjectDropdown.vue",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "ProjectDropdown.vue",
      "filePath": "frontend/src/components/work/ProjectDropdown.vue",
      "summary": "项目分组下拉选择器：展示已有项目列表支持切换，内嵌新建项目弹窗并通过 worksApi 持久化。",
      "tags": ["vue-component", "project", "dropdown", "create-modal"],
      "complexity": "simple",
      "languageNotes": "挂载时调用 worksApi.listProjects() 获取项目列表，新建后重新拉取更新选项。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:frontend/src/components/work/StageSelector.vue",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "StageSelector.vue",
      "filePath": "frontend/src/components/work/StageSelector.vue",
      "summary": "作品阶段选择器：根据文件类型动态获取对应阶段列表（如插画阶段、视频阶段），支持按阶段高亮配色。",
      "tags": ["vue-component", "stage", "workflow", "file-type"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:frontend/src/components/work/TagInput.vue",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "TagInput.vue",
      "filePath": "frontend/src/components/work/TagInput.vue",
      "summary": "标签输入组件：支持键盘导航的标签添加/移除，带建议下拉和 Enter/Backspace 快捷键操作。",
      "tags": ["vue-component", "tag-input", "autocomplete", "keyboard-nav"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 TagItem 类型从 useTagInput composable 导入，支持 ArrowUp/ArrowDown 键盘导航选择建议。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:frontend/src/components/work/WorkEditPanel.vue",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "WorkEditPanel.vue",
      "filePath": "frontend/src/components/work/WorkEditPanel.vue",
      "summary": "作品编辑侧边面板：集中管理作品基础信息、权利信息、阶段管理、项目归属和标签，组合使用 LicenseSelector/ProjectDropdown/StageSelector/TagInput 子组件。",
      "tags": ["vue-component", "work-edit", "form", "rights", "composite-component"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "通过 reactive 管理表单双向绑定，watch 监听 work prop 变化同步右侧面板，emit 保存事件携带结构化后的所有字段。"
    },
